title: C1_V2
description:
The Vaults of Terra bow to pressure and bring you the much anticipated lore video of the Blood Ravens and their mysterious past.

Also, Ed's opinion on the Chapter itself. *Dons flack armour*

Vaults of Terra Intro:
Stealth Shock

Intro Music: 
Daniel Yount - Dark Times
